divs: Sighting DetailsI was walking home from a friend's house as i passed though the park area, I spotted what I thought was a star, I stopped to look at it, the "star" began to move north-east in a slow pace.It stopped then hovered for a minute or so. It suddenly zipped off to the right and I lost sight of it from there. I assume it dissapeared.
Summary: walking home spotted a star like object
